1
00:01:50,520 --> 00:01:53,280
Fine, then I should thank you.

2
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:55,280
Thank you, Meng.

3
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,000
You're welcome.

4
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,280
By the way,

5
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,320
in my spare time,

6
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:35,640
I've been selling insurance for over ten years.

7
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:38,840
Time was too tight at the parent-teacher meeting that day.

8
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:41,440
I didn't get to explain it to your mom carefully.

9
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:44,300
I recommend they buy a critical illness insurance.

10
00:02:44,480 --> 00:02:46,680
This insurance is very beneficial.

11
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:48,160
When you go to college,

12
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,760
you'll be far away and won't be able to look after them.

13
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:52,820
With this insurance, everyone will have peace of mind.

14
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:53,720
By the way,

15
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:56,000
I have two contracts here.

16
00:02:56,160 --> 00:02:57,960
Take them home for your parents to look at.

17
00:02:57,960 --> 00:03:00,640
If they have any questions, they can ask me anytime,

18
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:01,280
okay?

19
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:03,240
Auntie, you're right.

20
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:05,420
I'll find time to talk to them.

21
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:08,160
Great.

22
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:10,160
Look how sensible he is.

23
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:11,640
Come, let's eat.

24
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:12,520
No contract today.

25
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:13,120
Let's just eat.

26
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,120
Take it with you when you leave.

27
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,200
Jingu, eat more.

28
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:16,920
Have some more.

29
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:20,760
Let's eat.

30
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:31,480
Well, deskmate.

31
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:33,440
About what my mom said today,

32
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,200
she was just saying it casually.

33
00:03:35,200 --> 00:03:36,360
Don't take it to heart.

34
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:38,520
Can I come over at 1:00 PM on Saturday?

35
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:42,400
I think so.

36
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,920
It's fine if you don't come.

37
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,400
Don't come. It's okay.

38
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:48,600
Yuanbao,

39
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,240
I know

40
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:53,360
you are still mad at me about what happened that day.

41
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:55,320
I wanted to explain it to you afterwards,

42
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:56,600
but the situation was a bit complicated.

43
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:58,200
I didn't know how to tell you,

44
00:03:58,520 --> 00:04:00,650
so I didn't contact you for a long time.

45
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:02,160
But Yuanbao, please believe me.

46
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:03,090
I had my reasons.

47
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,800
I didn't do it on purpose.

48
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:05,680
So,

49
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:08,720
please don't be mad at me anymore, okay?

50
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:10,520
I understand.

51
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:14,810
It's just that everyone was a bit disappointed at that time.

52
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:19,300
I'll come over for tutoring on Saturday.

53
00:04:23,840 --> 00:04:25,520
See you on Saturday then.

54
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:28,000
Thank you for the trouble.

55
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:29,860
No trouble at all. I'd love to.

56
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,200
Since your mom said so,

57
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:35,360
don't forget to join us on Saturday.

58
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:39,000
Sure. I want to see how you teach.

59
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:42,000
Then you can teach if I get something wrong.

60
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:43,800
I wouldn't dare.

61
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,880
You are so good at studying.

62
00:04:48,440 --> 00:04:51,080
What's wrong with you two?

63
00:04:52,840 --> 00:04:53,480
Yuanbao,

64
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:56,280
get some rest. I'll go back now.

65
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:57,400
See you on Saturday.

66
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:58,040
Bye.

67
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,890
Did you step on my foot just now?

68
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:11,600
Not me.

69
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:13,240
It was you.

70
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:14,360
Don't run.

71
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,360
You stepped on my foot. Why did you do that?

72
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:17,480
Stop right there.

73
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:21,920
If you were like this before,

74
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:24,160
wouldn't your grades have improved long ago?

75
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:26,720
And you wouldn't score worse than me every time.

76
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,480
You're obviously a physics genius.

77
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,360
Why do you pretend to know nothing

78
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,520
in class?

79
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:31,640
You didn't cheat on the physics exam.

80
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:32,700
Why did you admit it

81
00:05:32,880 --> 00:05:34,200
and say you copied mine?

82
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:35,130
What do you mean?

83
00:05:35,320 --> 00:05:36,380
Why did you do that?

84
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:38,920
Alright. Let's see how you explain it.

85
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:41,880
If I'm wrong, you tell me.

86
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,680
Jingu, what a coincidence.

87
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:52,080
I was just about to knock.

88
00:05:52,840 --> 00:05:54,400
Are you going out?

89
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:55,560
Didn't we agree

90
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,840
you'd tutor me today?

91
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,120
Xinrui.

92
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,960
Sorry, I forgot.

93
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:02,940
How about I tutor you when I get back tonight?

94
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:05,290
Do you have something important to do?

95
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,600
Do you need my help?

96
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,600
No, thanks.

97
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,040
You should go back and rest first.

98
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:12,100
I'll call you when I get back tonight.

99
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:13,320
Okay.

100
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:15,320
Then I'll wait for your call.

101
00:06:15,640 --> 00:06:17,720
Okay, I'll get going. Bye.

102
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:21,260
Remember to close the door for me.

103
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:31,880
Tutoring?

104
00:06:32,520 --> 00:06:33,240
Well,

105
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:36,090
you don't mind if I join, do you?

106
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,840
Why are you so late?

107
00:06:38,960 --> 00:06:40,490
I've been waiting for ages.

108
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:43,080
I just went to the restroom.

109
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:45,200
Here.

110
00:06:45,640 --> 00:06:46,520
Move over a bit.

111
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:49,480
My grades are poor. I need to be closer to Jingu.

112
00:06:59,000 --> 00:06:59,720
Go ahead.

113
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:06,730
A skydiver is doing a low-altitude performance.

114
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:09,080
When the plane is 224 meters above the ground,

115
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:10,360
flying horizontally,

116
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:12,400
the skydiver leaves the plane

117
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:15,040
and free falls in the vertical direction.

118
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:18,240
Come on, have some fruit.

119
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:24,320
Do you both like strawberries?

120
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,760
I'll go get some more.

121
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:33,320
Let me tell you.

122
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:35,280
Even though Yuanbao forgave you,

123
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:36,520
I haven't.

124
00:07:36,880 --> 00:07:38,720
If you hadn't stood her up,

125
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,800
her performance wouldn't have been placed last,

126
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,930
and her eye wouldn't have gotten hurt.

127
00:07:43,159 --> 00:07:44,820
You have a guilty conscience.

128
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,320
You were afraid I'd go to your house

129
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:48,050
and expose your big lie, right?

130
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:50,409
What are you talking about?

131
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:04,020
What are you doing?

132
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,380
Are you going to fight?

133
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:17,200
Walk Jingu downstairs properly

134
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:18,560
and let him take the fruit back.

135
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,360
Hear me?

136
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:25,480
Jingu, thanks for your hard work today.

137
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:27,760
Come over often to tutor them.

138
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,800
You two young men

139
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:32,120
should be good friends, okay?

140
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:34,200
Don't worry, Auntie. We will.

141
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,240
Go on.

142
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:39,440
Jingu, text me when you get home.

143
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:40,809
Don't worry.

144
00:08:40,919 --> 00:08:41,760
Bye, Auntie.

145
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:00,280
Make up.

146
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:07,360
Stop messing around.

147
00:09:07,400 --> 00:09:08,240
Go up quickly.

148
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:27,500
Apologize.

149
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,000
I'm sorry.

150
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:31,200
And what else?

151
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:35,440
Love you.

152
00:09:37,160 --> 00:09:37,880
Sing.

153
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:45,200
Because we are family.

154
00:09:57,560 --> 00:09:58,490
Where did you go?

155
00:09:58,800 --> 00:10:00,400
Why did you come back so late?

156
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:04,650
Since the last drama performance,

157
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:07,120
you've been giving me the cold shoulder for days.

158
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:08,200
If Xinrui hadn't

159
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:10,130
been putting in a good word for you,

160
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:12,160
would you have ignored me for the rest of your life?

161
00:10:12,160 --> 00:10:13,680
Do you know that Xinrui

162
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:15,720
has been waiting for you at home all day today?

163
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:16,600
Didn't you promise

164
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:17,880
to tutor her?

165
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:20,920
You two are childhood sweethearts.

166
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:23,240
Xinrui is a British citizen now,

167
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:25,170
and just came back from abroad.

168
00:10:25,280 --> 00:10:27,080
You need to take good care of her.

169
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:30,050
When you have time, you should tutor her well.

170
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:32,040
Only a good girl like Xinrui

171
00:10:32,160 --> 00:10:33,560
and a family like hers

172
00:10:33,680 --> 00:10:35,480
can truly help you in the future.

173
00:10:36,880 --> 00:10:37,760
Did you hear me?

174
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:39,740
Did you hear me talking to you?

175
00:10:42,520 --> 00:10:43,840
Don't be mad.

176
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:47,360
Jingu,

177
00:10:48,040 --> 00:10:50,640
what's with this medical insurance contract?

178
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:54,680
I asked a classmate's parent for it.

179
00:10:54,760 --> 00:10:56,120
I think you should buy it.

180
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:57,380
A classmate's parent?

181
00:10:57,840 --> 00:10:59,640
Is it the mother of that Yuanbao?

182
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:00,400
Yes.

183
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:02,640
What kind of family is this?

184
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:04,680
They just want you to spend money.

185
00:11:04,680 --> 00:11:06,640
They probably want you to buy a house.

186
00:11:06,640 --> 00:11:08,440
Medical insurance is all the same.

187
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:09,640
It's the same wherever you buy it.

188
00:11:09,640 --> 00:11:10,920
How is it the same?

189
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:14,640
If you buy it, you should buy it from someone with high quality, high education,

190
00:11:14,640 --> 00:11:16,080
and high income.

191
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:17,810
That way, it's guaranteed.

192
00:11:21,640 --> 00:11:23,560
I'm tired. I'm going back to rest.

193
00:11:25,560 --> 00:11:26,320
Jingu.

194
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:30,720
Don't be mad.

195
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:49,080
Xiong Yuanbao, come on!

196
00:11:58,440 --> 00:11:59,700
Come, let's go inside.

197
00:12:01,040 --> 00:12:02,570
Why don't you ride the bike?

198
00:12:03,920 --> 00:12:05,760
You're already this dizzy walking.

199
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:07,880
It would be worse on the back of a bike.

200
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:09,570
Let's take a taxi later.

201
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:10,920
A taxi?

202
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:13,600
No, it's too expensive.

203
00:12:13,680 --> 00:12:14,880
I have to save money.

204
00:12:16,280 --> 00:12:17,920
What for?

205
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:19,040
Of course,

206
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:24,720
to see Jay Chou's concert.

207
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:28,280
In that case,

208
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:30,560
you can't be late for school tomorrow.

209
00:12:30,560 --> 00:12:32,800
Don't show up just in time for lunch.

210
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,160
No, stop.

211
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:38,800
I'm a little dizzy right now.

212
00:12:39,760 --> 00:12:40,600
Come on.

213
00:12:42,560 --> 00:12:43,240
Sit here.

214
00:12:48,680 --> 00:12:49,560
Come, stand up.

215
00:12:50,760 --> 00:12:51,320
Stand up.

216
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:53,360
Step up here.

217
00:12:58,360 --> 00:12:59,000
What?

218
00:12:59,280 --> 00:13:00,200
I'll carry you on my back.

219
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,200
Why?

220
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:03,000
I'm not lame or blind.

221
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:05,520
Just be good and listen to me.

222
00:13:10,520 --> 00:13:11,080
Yuanbao.

223
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,280
What is it?

224
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:19,000
Why did you call me and say nothing?

225
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:21,600
Nothing.

226
00:13:23,880 --> 00:13:25,520
So mysterious.

227
00:13:31,160 --> 00:13:32,200
Put me down.

228
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:38,320
Yuanbao.

229
00:13:38,640 --> 00:13:39,400
Yuanbao.

230
00:13:41,040 --> 00:13:42,040
Why are you here?

231
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:43,690
Do your eyes still hurt?

232
00:13:44,160 --> 00:13:44,840
I'm fine.

233
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,920
Didn't I text you about it?

234
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,560
Let me help you.

235
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:54,810
I didn't see it with my own eyes.

236
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:56,240
I was so worried.

237
00:13:58,760 --> 00:14:00,440
Pirates of the Caribbean!

238
00:14:00,520 --> 00:14:01,480
Wow, big shot.

239
00:14:01,560 --> 00:14:03,360
You even brought a bodyguard.

240
00:14:03,640 --> 00:14:05,170
What are you talking about?

241
00:14:05,680 --> 00:14:07,320
Yuanbao, with your eyes painted like this,

242
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:08,520
can you even see?

243
00:14:08,760 --> 00:14:09,960
You look a bit like...

244
00:14:10,400 --> 00:14:11,920
Zhu, zhu, zhu...

245
00:14:11,960 --> 00:14:12,920
Zhu what?

246
00:14:13,800 --> 00:14:15,720
Angelina Jolie.

247
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:16,900
Right, that Jolie.

248
00:14:18,640 --> 00:14:20,440
Remember to take your medicine.

249
00:14:26,480 --> 00:14:27,120
Go back.

250
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:31,680
Yuanbao is back.

251
00:14:31,680 --> 00:14:32,560
When did you get back?

252
00:14:32,560 --> 00:14:32,960
Just now.

253
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:33,560
Really?

254
00:14:35,680 --> 00:14:36,610
Yuanbao is back.

255
00:14:36,920 --> 00:14:38,920
Let's applaud and welcome her back.

256
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:47,920
Class, Yuanbao

257
00:14:48,040 --> 00:14:49,520
fought for the honor of our class

258
00:14:49,520 --> 00:14:50,650
in this competition

259
00:14:50,680 --> 00:14:51,680
and was accidentally injured.

260
00:14:51,680 --> 00:14:53,360
Good thing it only hurt the eyelid.

261
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:54,200
So I am here

262
00:14:54,240 --> 00:14:55,320
to remind everyone that

263
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:56,640
during the three years of high school,

264
00:14:56,640 --> 00:14:58,640
health and safety are the most important.

265
00:14:58,640 --> 00:14:59,200
I hope everyone

266
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:00,600
in your daily lives

267
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:01,960
will pay attention to safety.

268
00:15:01,960 --> 00:15:02,820
Did you hear me?

269
00:15:03,040 --> 00:15:04,240
Yes.

270
00:15:04,680 --> 00:15:06,840
There's something I must say.

271
00:15:07,520 --> 00:15:08,450
Unfortunately,

272
00:15:08,640 --> 00:15:10,000
our class's performance

273
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:12,130
wasn't selected in this competition.

274
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:14,280
However,

275
00:15:14,520 --> 00:15:15,400
an enthusiastic viewer

276
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:16,930
uploaded our video online,

277
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:19,860
and the views have already exceeded three million.

278
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:21,400
Many enthusiastic viewers

279
00:15:21,400 --> 00:15:23,530
say you have a great talent for acting,

280
00:15:23,640 --> 00:15:26,100
and that you performed exceptionally well.

281
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:26,800
Okay.

282
00:15:30,680 --> 00:15:32,140
Through this experience,

283
00:15:32,280 --> 00:15:33,740
I want to tell everyone...

284
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:34,840
Sometimes,

285
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:36,320
winning or losing isn't that important.

286
00:15:36,320 --> 00:15:38,920
As long as you participate, you will gain something.

287
00:15:38,920 --> 00:15:41,360
Don't be overly joyful over gains or sad over losses.

288
00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:43,520
Success is just a matter of time, okay?

289
00:15:43,760 --> 00:15:45,360
Okay.

290
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:49,160
Okay, then.

291
00:15:49,240 --> 00:15:51,240
Study by yourselves for this class.

292
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:58,000
Is it ugly?

293
00:15:58,280 --> 00:15:59,940
You mean the eye on your gauze?

294
00:16:00,760 --> 00:16:01,960
Compared to your eye,

295
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:04,320
it's really not that good-looking.

296
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:05,600
Actually,

297
00:16:05,880 --> 00:16:07,960
you really didn't have to rush to class.

298
00:16:07,960 --> 00:16:10,400
I'll tutor you on the weekend anyway.

299
00:16:11,640 --> 00:16:13,120
It's so boring at home.

300
00:16:13,520 --> 00:16:14,600
I'd rather come to school.

301
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:16,600
It's more fun to stay with everyone.

302
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:23,280
How is it?

303
00:16:34,320 --> 00:16:36,120
Doctor, what's wrong?

304
00:16:36,800 --> 00:16:38,520
Is my face ruined?

305
00:16:38,880 --> 00:16:40,760
Am I ugly now?

306
00:16:41,040 --> 00:16:42,760
Her skin is healing very well,

307
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:44,320
leaving no scars.

308
00:16:44,400 --> 00:16:45,680
It's really a blessing.

309
00:16:45,680 --> 00:16:48,010
But you must be more careful in the future.

310
00:16:48,160 --> 00:16:49,320
Thank you, Doctor.

311
00:16:49,560 --> 00:16:51,200
Thank you, doctor. Thanks for your hard work.

312
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:51,840
You're welcome.

313
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:53,680
Everything is fine. You can go back.

314
00:16:53,680 --> 00:16:54,480
Okay.

315
00:16:55,040 --> 00:16:56,120
Look at you.

316
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:57,400
It was so dangerous this time.

317
00:16:57,400 --> 00:16:58,560
You were lucky.

318
00:16:58,640 --> 00:17:00,280
We were worried to death.

319
00:17:00,680 --> 00:17:01,360
Yeah.

320
00:17:01,800 --> 00:17:03,000
From now on, you and Qingyun

321
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:04,640
should focus on your studies.

322
00:17:04,640 --> 00:17:06,640
Don't participate in other activities.

323
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:08,440
The final exams are coming soon.

324
00:17:09,079 --> 00:17:10,880
Let Meng Jingu tutor you again.

325
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:13,040
Got it.

326
00:17:18,960 --> 00:17:21,599
Goodbye, teacher.

327
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:24,680
Ruirui, let's go get the workbooks.

328
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:27,520
Yuanbao.

329
00:17:27,599 --> 00:17:28,760
Do you want to go for a walk?

330
00:17:28,760 --> 00:17:30,160
We can chat along the way.

331
00:17:30,760 --> 00:17:31,520
Sure.

332
00:17:31,800 --> 00:17:32,480
Let's go.

333
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:36,140
What's wrong, Xinrui?

334
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:39,280
I was in a hurry to notify you at the theater that day.

335
00:17:39,280 --> 00:17:40,810
I accidentally fell again.

336
00:17:41,080 --> 00:17:43,040
Then let me go with you to the infirmary.

337
00:17:43,040 --> 00:17:43,640
It's fine.

338
00:17:43,880 --> 00:17:46,400
It's inconvenient for you with your injured eye.

339
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:47,200
Jingu.

340
00:17:47,520 --> 00:17:49,450
Can you go to the infirmary with me?

341
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:51,760
Yuanbao.

342
00:17:51,960 --> 00:17:53,560
I'll go to the infirmary with Xinrui.

343
00:17:53,560 --> 00:17:55,960
Ask for leave for us when the teacher comes.

344
00:18:02,560 --> 00:18:04,720
Then we'll talk when we get back.

345
00:18:05,520 --> 00:18:06,240
Okay.

346
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:07,690
We're leaving then.

347
00:18:07,720 --> 00:18:08,520
Okay.

348
00:18:17,920 --> 00:18:18,680
Xinrui,

349
00:18:19,080 --> 00:18:21,080
is your back injury feeling better?

350
00:18:21,360 --> 00:18:22,090
Much better.

351
00:18:22,680 --> 00:18:24,410
Old injuries take time to heal.

352
00:18:25,360 --> 00:18:26,640
Your eye is better too.

353
00:18:26,800 --> 00:18:28,930
It's great that it didn't leave a scar.

354
00:18:29,440 --> 00:18:30,880
Yeah, I was really lucky.

355
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:33,760
If you need any help in the future,

356
00:18:33,760 --> 00:18:34,690
just let me know.

357
00:18:35,080 --> 00:18:36,440
It's fine. I have Jingu.

358
00:18:36,560 --> 00:18:37,760
He can take care of me.

359
00:18:38,800 --> 00:18:39,560
Okay.

360
00:18:40,520 --> 00:18:41,120
By the way,

361
00:18:41,680 --> 00:18:43,160
actually, the day you just came back,

362
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:44,360
I wanted to tell you.

363
00:18:44,840 --> 00:18:46,700
But my back injury acted up again,

364
00:18:46,800 --> 00:18:48,460
so I didn't have time to say it.

365
00:18:48,520 --> 00:18:49,440
What is it?

366
00:18:50,440 --> 00:18:51,280
Well,

367
00:18:51,560 --> 00:18:54,090
I don't want you to misunderstand Meng Jingu.

368
00:18:54,280 --> 00:18:57,800
Actually, he couldn't go to the live performance that day

369
00:18:58,440 --> 00:18:59,840
because he had no choice.

370
00:19:00,880 --> 00:19:02,520
Jingu was locked up that day.

371
00:19:04,040 --> 00:19:05,360
Locked up?

372
00:19:07,200 --> 00:19:08,520
Uncle Meng doesn't like it

373
00:19:08,520 --> 00:19:10,680
when he participates in activities unrelated to his studies,

374
00:19:10,680 --> 00:19:12,120
so he is very strict with him.

375
00:19:12,120 --> 00:19:14,600
So I hope you won't misunderstand him

376
00:19:15,280 --> 00:19:16,800
or blame him. Okay?

377
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:21,040
Although I knew he had his difficulties,

378
00:19:21,560 --> 00:19:22,420
I didn't expect

379
00:19:22,480 --> 00:19:24,440
that something like this would happen that day.

380
00:19:24,440 --> 00:19:27,320
Xinrui, thank you for telling me this.

381
00:19:28,360 --> 00:19:29,080
No problem.

382
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:31,340
Jingu is the kind of person

383
00:19:31,360 --> 00:19:33,080
who really values his friends.

384
00:19:33,080 --> 00:19:34,540
He mentions you to me a lot.

385
00:19:34,680 --> 00:19:36,680
He says you're straightforward, loyal,

386
00:19:36,680 --> 00:19:37,940
and a good buddy of his.

387
00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:41,220
So he doesn't want any misunderstandings between you two.

388
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:42,760
A good buddy.

389
00:19:46,040 --> 00:19:47,240
He's just like that.

390
00:19:47,840 --> 00:19:49,960
Ever since we were kids, whenever he's misunderstood,

391
00:19:49,960 --> 00:19:51,420
he never defends himself.

392
00:19:52,080 --> 00:19:53,920
So I have to speak up for Jingu.

393
00:19:54,680 --> 00:19:58,680
Did Meng Jingu ask you to tell me this?

394
00:19:59,360 --> 00:20:00,280
No, he didn't.

395
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:03,600
But whenever this happened in the past,

396
00:20:03,880 --> 00:20:06,140
I was always the one to sort it out for him.

397
00:20:06,240 --> 00:20:09,100
I've lost count of how many times since we were kids.

398
00:20:09,560 --> 00:20:10,560
I'm used to it.

399
00:20:11,280 --> 00:20:14,080
I wonder how many people

400
00:20:15,360 --> 00:20:18,020
Jingu has offended during the year I was abroad.

401
00:20:20,200 --> 00:20:21,240
So, Yuanbao,

402
00:20:22,560 --> 00:20:24,880
you're not mad at Jingu anymore, right?

403
00:20:25,760 --> 00:20:26,640
Of course not.

404
00:20:28,320 --> 00:20:29,720
That puts my mind at ease.

405
00:20:30,240 --> 00:20:30,960
Yuanbao.

406
00:20:31,160 --> 00:20:32,880
If he does anything wrong again in the future,

407
00:20:32,880 --> 00:20:33,640
just tell me.

408
00:20:33,760 --> 00:20:35,960
I'll teach Jingu a lesson for you, okay?

409
00:20:37,040 --> 00:20:37,680
Okay.

410
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:41,560
Xinrui, is there anything else?

411
00:20:41,920 --> 00:20:44,120
If not, I'll head back first.

412
00:20:44,840 --> 00:20:45,640
Nothing else.

413
00:20:45,720 --> 00:20:47,050
Let's go back together.

414
00:20:52,720 --> 00:20:54,980
What's wrong? Does your back hurt again?

415
00:20:55,680 --> 00:20:56,540
Let me help you.

416
00:20:58,080 --> 00:20:59,280
Thank you, Yuanbao.

417
00:20:59,640 --> 00:21:00,640
You're so loyal.

418
00:21:00,800 --> 00:21:03,000
No wonder boys like being your bros.

419
00:21:04,640 --> 00:21:05,520
Then let's

420
00:21:05,800 --> 00:21:06,960
be good sisters.

421
00:21:09,160 --> 00:21:10,040
Sure.

422
00:21:12,360 --> 00:21:12,960
Slow down.

423
00:21:26,680 --> 00:21:29,920
Deskmate, Xinrui came to me today

424
00:21:30,000 --> 00:21:32,800
and told me what happened on the day of the competition.

425
00:21:32,800 --> 00:21:35,040
I didn't expect things to be like that.

426
00:21:35,320 --> 00:21:37,200
I was even mad at you then.

427
00:21:37,560 --> 00:21:38,800
I'm really sorry.

428
00:21:43,640 --> 00:21:44,360
Yuanbao.

429
00:21:44,720 --> 00:21:46,380
Thank you for understanding.

430
00:21:46,400 --> 00:21:48,860
I've never been good at opening up to others,

431
00:21:48,880 --> 00:21:51,120
nor am I used to talking about family matters.

432
00:21:51,120 --> 00:21:52,080
So,

433
00:21:52,280 --> 00:21:54,640
failing to explain things clearly to you in time

434
00:21:54,640 --> 00:21:55,800
was my fault.

435
00:21:57,720 --> 00:21:59,080
Everyone has things

436
00:21:59,120 --> 00:22:01,240
they don't want to confide in others.

437
00:22:01,680 --> 00:22:02,720
I understand.

438
00:22:03,440 --> 00:22:06,500
But keeping things bottled up for too long gets tiring.

439
00:22:07,720 --> 00:22:09,240
Thank you for understanding.

440
00:22:09,240 --> 00:22:12,640
Can I talk to you when I have something on my mind in the future?

441
00:22:17,520 --> 00:22:19,480
Sure. We can help each other.

442
00:22:19,560 --> 00:22:22,200
Then don't find me annoying later.

443
00:22:24,200 --> 00:22:25,280
Okay.

444
00:22:29,880 --> 00:22:31,840
I wonder what Gu Xinrui

445
00:22:31,920 --> 00:22:33,720
wanted to talk to me about today.

446
00:22:34,080 --> 00:22:36,160
It's always good to text back.

447
00:22:47,680 --> 00:22:49,610
I can't believe I ran into you here.

448
00:22:50,000 --> 00:22:51,200
What a rare occasion.

449
00:22:51,760 --> 00:22:53,320
It's a small world.

450
00:22:54,480 --> 00:22:55,340
Xiong Yuanbao.

451
00:22:56,320 --> 00:22:57,960
I'm just really curious.

452
00:22:58,120 --> 00:22:58,960
Tell me,

453
00:22:59,320 --> 00:23:02,200
you seem to study hard every day,

454
00:23:03,320 --> 00:23:05,720
so why are your test scores always the same?

455
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:08,880
And you just goof around every day.

456
00:23:09,240 --> 00:23:10,920
Aren't you worried?

457
00:23:13,840 --> 00:23:16,170
You wouldn't understand a fairy's world.

458
00:23:16,320 --> 00:23:17,640
A fairy's world?

459
00:23:19,000 --> 00:23:21,600
Did this fairy land face-first?

460
00:23:22,560 --> 00:23:24,490
Xiong Yuanbao, as your classmate,

461
00:23:24,520 --> 00:23:26,080
let me give you a piece of advice.

462
00:23:26,080 --> 00:23:28,080
If you want to be on Meng Jingu's level,

463
00:23:28,080 --> 00:23:29,400
you have to study hard.

464
00:23:29,800 --> 00:23:32,080
Don't act like that naive Tong Ruirui all day,

465
00:23:32,080 --> 00:23:34,040
doing nothing but reading romance novels.

466
00:23:34,040 --> 00:23:37,200
Can reading those get you a college acceptance letter?

467
00:23:38,320 --> 00:23:40,520
Can they win you the heart of your crush?

468
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:42,760
Idol dramas and romance novels

469
00:23:43,400 --> 00:23:45,600
are just meant to trick ignorant girls.

470
00:23:46,320 --> 00:23:47,320
What is reality?

471
00:23:48,120 --> 00:23:50,050
A strong alliance between equals,

472
00:23:50,360 --> 00:23:52,520
like Gu Xinrui and Meng Jingu.

473
00:23:53,400 --> 00:23:54,460
Do you understand?

474
00:23:56,680 --> 00:23:58,280
Just mind your own business.

475
00:23:58,400 --> 00:24:00,680
You're taking my good intentions for ill will.

476
00:24:00,680 --> 00:24:02,140
Whatever, suit yourself.

477
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:07,680
Look at you.

478
00:24:08,440 --> 00:24:09,440
You have no shame.

479
00:24:12,840 --> 00:24:13,900
What are you doing?

480
00:24:14,200 --> 00:24:16,200
As your classmate, I'm kindly reminding you,

481
00:24:16,200 --> 00:24:17,530
you've got your period.

482
00:24:22,040 --> 00:24:23,900
Let me go to the restroom with you.

483
00:24:32,640 --> 00:24:33,400
Thanks.

484
00:24:37,240 --> 00:24:38,170
What did you say?

485
00:24:39,920 --> 00:24:40,880
I said,

486
00:24:42,440 --> 00:24:44,880
thank you for buying this for me

487
00:24:45,520 --> 00:24:47,200
and lending me your jacket.

488
00:24:50,280 --> 00:24:52,160
Now that you've seen me make a fool of myself,

489
00:24:52,160 --> 00:24:54,360
you must be feeling pretty smug, right?

490
00:24:55,280 --> 00:24:58,000
It's the first time I've heard you say thank you.

491
00:24:58,800 --> 00:25:00,130
I just found it strange.

492
00:25:06,680 --> 00:25:07,360
Qiao Yan,

493
00:25:08,040 --> 00:25:11,040
why are you always like a hedgehog towards me?

494
00:25:12,440 --> 00:25:13,840
I just have it out for you.

495
00:25:14,600 --> 00:25:17,530
And don't think just because you helped me this time,

496
00:25:17,800 --> 00:25:20,130
I won't hold grudges against you anymore.

497
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:23,320
Qiao Yan,

498
00:25:25,760 --> 00:25:28,400
I think I know why.

499
00:25:29,360 --> 00:25:30,720
I'll tell you today.

500
00:25:31,200 --> 00:25:34,000
Everything I saw on the street that day,

501
00:25:34,880 --> 00:25:36,840
I haven't told anyone.

502
00:25:44,960 --> 00:25:45,760
I know.

503
00:25:48,680 --> 00:25:49,440
Thank you.

504
00:25:51,480 --> 00:25:52,120
By the way,

505
00:25:53,000 --> 00:25:53,800
in the future,

506
00:25:54,400 --> 00:25:55,460
with your studies,

507
00:25:56,160 --> 00:25:57,720
if you have any problems,

508
00:25:59,200 --> 00:26:00,200
you can come to me.

509
00:26:01,440 --> 00:26:02,440
I'll be going now.

510
00:26:18,840 --> 00:26:20,240
Dad, be careful.

511
00:26:21,240 --> 00:26:22,320
Let me go.

512
00:26:23,080 --> 00:26:24,840
Why aren't you going home to do your homework?

513
00:26:24,840 --> 00:26:26,240
Why are you following me?

514
00:26:26,360 --> 00:26:27,800
Dad, hurry up and leave.

515
00:26:29,760 --> 00:26:31,090
If you don't study hard,

516
00:26:31,600 --> 00:26:34,000
do you want to end up like me today?

517
00:26:34,680 --> 00:26:35,480
Dad, let's go home.

518
00:26:35,480 --> 00:26:36,160
Get up.

519
00:26:36,400 --> 00:26:37,880
Did you hear me?

520
00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:39,040
Get lost.

521
00:26:39,680 --> 00:26:41,320
Why did you hit my classmate?

522
00:26:44,040 --> 00:26:45,120
He is my dad.

523
00:27:04,280 --> 00:27:05,160
I'm sorry.

524
00:27:05,640 --> 00:27:08,320
The doctor said I can't move around too much with my back injury,

525
00:27:08,320 --> 00:27:11,560
so I have to stay in the classroom for lunch.

526
00:27:11,960 --> 00:27:14,000
And it makes you have to stay here with me.

527
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:14,800
It's fine.

528
00:27:16,200 --> 00:27:16,960
I know

529
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:19,880
you hate it the most when Uncle Meng orders you around.

530
00:27:19,880 --> 00:27:23,010
This time when he told you to eat with me in the classroom,

531
00:27:23,240 --> 00:27:25,440
he probably used a commanding tone again.

532
00:27:25,440 --> 00:27:26,570
He's just like that.

533
00:27:28,760 --> 00:27:31,760
It was my mom who told the doctor not to let me move much.

534
00:27:31,800 --> 00:27:32,840
I think she probably

535
00:27:32,840 --> 00:27:34,680
when she was talking to Aunt Meng,

536
00:27:34,680 --> 00:27:36,140
mentioned it by accident.

537
00:27:37,080 --> 00:27:37,840
Let's eat.

538
00:27:38,560 --> 00:27:41,200
Even if my dad didn't say it, I'd still take care of you.

539
00:27:41,200 --> 00:27:43,330
We're basically siblings, after all.

540
00:27:49,160 --> 00:27:52,290
I specially asked our maid to make your favorite dishes.

541
00:27:52,600 --> 00:27:54,200
Didn't you used to say all the time

542
00:27:54,200 --> 00:27:55,600
that she was a great cook?

543
00:27:55,640 --> 00:27:56,800
During the years I was abroad,

544
00:27:56,800 --> 00:27:58,120
you didn't get to eat her cooking.

545
00:27:58,120 --> 00:27:58,800
Try it.

546
00:27:59,440 --> 00:27:59,920
Okay.

547
00:28:00,040 --> 00:28:02,520
This is really good.

548
00:28:06,080 --> 00:28:08,560
Are you still mad at me

549
00:28:08,640 --> 00:28:11,840
for leaving early to go abroad by myself?

550
00:28:12,240 --> 00:28:13,040
No.

551
00:28:14,280 --> 00:28:15,400
I know

552
00:28:15,680 --> 00:28:18,080
that for the sake of dance,

553
00:28:18,160 --> 00:28:19,690
I chose to leave you behind.

554
00:28:20,200 --> 00:28:22,560
Later, I injured my back abroad

555
00:28:22,800 --> 00:28:23,960
and came running back to you.

556
00:28:23,960 --> 00:28:25,240
I was wrong.

557
00:28:26,440 --> 00:28:27,520
But Jingu,

558
00:28:29,400 --> 00:28:31,440
you know how much effort and dedication

559
00:28:31,440 --> 00:28:33,280
I put into dancing.

560
00:28:34,760 --> 00:28:36,040
Now that dance is gone,

561
00:28:37,360 --> 00:28:38,680
I don't want my best friend

562
00:28:38,680 --> 00:28:40,080
to drift away from me too.

563
00:28:41,880 --> 00:28:42,680
Okay?

564
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:48,240
I'm not mad at you.

565
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:49,720
I can understand.

566
00:28:51,000 --> 00:28:52,060
It's just, Xinrui,

567
00:28:52,800 --> 00:28:53,800
we've grown up.

568
00:28:54,640 --> 00:28:56,280
We can't be like when we were kids

569
00:28:56,280 --> 00:28:57,800
and stick together all day.

570
00:28:57,800 --> 00:28:59,320
We both have our own lives.

571
00:29:00,000 --> 00:29:02,840
Drifting apart doesn't mean we're not close.

572
00:29:03,560 --> 00:29:04,360
It's just that

573
00:29:05,120 --> 00:29:07,180
we should both try to be independent.

574
00:29:09,480 --> 00:29:12,340
Take your time eating. I'm going to grab a document.

575
00:29:39,040 --> 00:29:39,760
Ruirui.

576
00:29:40,280 --> 00:29:41,740
Weren't you with Yuanbao?

577
00:29:41,840 --> 00:29:42,570
Where is she?

578
00:29:43,000 --> 00:29:44,600
Yuanbao went to the library.

579
00:29:44,640 --> 00:29:46,440
So I came to buy some food myself.

580
00:29:46,800 --> 00:29:48,800
She rarely goes to the library all year.

581
00:29:48,800 --> 00:29:50,260
Why the sudden whim today?

582
00:29:50,680 --> 00:29:51,560
She said...

583
00:29:52,040 --> 00:29:54,520
Finals are coming. She needs to cram.

584
00:29:56,920 --> 00:29:57,800
What is this?

585
00:29:59,640 --> 00:30:01,560
I don't think this big eater ate well at noon.

586
00:30:01,560 --> 00:30:02,960
So I bought her some feed.

587
00:30:03,040 --> 00:30:04,080
I'll take it to her now.

588
00:30:04,080 --> 00:30:05,740
Anyway, I'm going to find her.

589
00:30:10,720 --> 00:30:13,680
It's so great to have a brother like Qingyun.

590
00:30:48,560 --> 00:30:50,290
Aren't you going to grab a book?

591
00:30:56,000 --> 00:30:59,080
When did you get here? You scared me.

592
00:31:00,040 --> 00:31:01,100
I just got here too.

593
00:31:01,360 --> 00:31:02,760
What book did you choose?

594
00:31:05,040 --> 00:31:05,720
This one.

595
00:31:05,720 --> 00:31:06,600
Cyclic learning, memorize until you know it, guaranteed effect!

596
00:31:06,600 --> 00:31:07,730
I've read this book.

597
00:31:08,080 --> 00:31:11,480
The content is a bit too general, so it's not very suitable for you.

598
00:31:11,480 --> 00:31:12,340
How about this?

599
00:31:12,720 --> 00:31:15,250
Later, based on your ability and foundation,

600
00:31:15,480 --> 00:31:17,000
I'll organize a specific set of

601
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:18,460
physics concepts for you.

602
00:31:18,720 --> 00:31:20,280
It will be more targeted

603
00:31:20,400 --> 00:31:21,440
and more suitable for you.

604
00:31:21,440 --> 00:31:22,200
Really?

605
00:31:22,360 --> 00:31:23,040
Of course.

606
00:31:24,440 --> 00:31:25,600
You read this first.

607
00:31:25,880 --> 00:31:28,120
I'll go pick out a few other materials for you.

608
00:31:28,120 --> 00:31:28,980
As for this one,

609
00:31:30,160 --> 00:31:31,020
just forget it.

610
00:31:54,840 --> 00:31:56,280
Did Mutou buy this?

611
00:31:56,600 --> 00:31:58,040
Why didn't he say anything?
